cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP input streams to 0 will cause SCTP connection establishment failure and prevent proper communication between CU and AMF.

du.explanation_en: Setting SCTP input streams to 0 will cause SCTP connection establishment failure and prevent proper communication between DU and CU.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SCTP 輸入流設定為 0 會導致 SCTP 連接建立失敗，並阻止 DU 與 CU 之間的正確通信。
